WEBVTT

00:12.097 --> 00:13.556
[Ray]
Previously on  Ray Donovan...

00:13.556 --> 00:14.807
I know what you're up to,
Mr. Donovan,

00:14.807 --> 00:16.392
selling coke
and running girls.

00:16.392 --> 00:17.893
Working with us
is the only way

00:17.893 --> 00:19.270
you and your kids are
coming out of this

00:19.270 --> 00:22.690
with all your arms and legs
still attached.

00:22.690 --> 00:24.400
I'd like you to start
helping again.

00:24.400 --> 00:26.026
Who's he ratting on?

00:26.026 --> 00:28.154
It's the Minassians,
Armenian mafia.

00:28.154 --> 00:30.281
Mickey's been getting money
from them for a while now.

00:30.281 --> 00:32.032
Jesus Christ.

00:32.032 --> 00:35.245
[Mickey] I'm fucked.
They made me wear a wire.

00:35.245 --> 00:36.912
Mr. Donovan.

00:36.912 --> 00:38.414
[Mickey] In three days,
I'm supposed to buy sex slaves

00:38.414 --> 00:41.208
off a cargo container
in San Pedro.

00:41.208 --> 00:43.627
They're gonna kill me.
I need help.

00:43.627 --> 00:45.088
Shit!
Mick, get down!

00:45.088 --> 00:47.090
[gunfire]

00:49.967 --> 00:51.094
[Mickey]
Terry's been shot, Ray.

00:51.094 --> 00:52.344
Get me a priest.

00:52.344 --> 00:54.680
Those Minassians
aren't gonna stop.

00:54.680 --> 00:55.973
Fuck.
Let's go.

00:56.974 --> 00:58.268
[yells]

01:00.936 --> 01:02.688
[Ray]
You gotta leave L.A.

01:02.688 --> 01:04.274
I'm tired of worrying
about my family 'cause of you.

01:04.274 --> 01:05.149
You gotta go.

01:05.149 --> 01:07.067
[Romero] Ray?

01:07.067 --> 01:10.279
[Ray] My brother, Terry,
he needs a priest. He got shot.

01:10.279 --> 01:12.615
Confess your sins.

01:12.615 --> 01:14.533
I killed Father O'Connor.

01:14.533 --> 01:16.285
[Romero] Why, Ray?
Why did you do it?

01:16.285 --> 01:18.329
The things he did.

01:18.329 --> 01:21.291
After a while,
I stopped fighting him.

01:21.291 --> 01:22.875
[Romero] He shouldn't
have done that to you, Ray.

01:22.875 --> 01:24.126
You were just a boy.

01:24.126 --> 01:26.545
You asked God
for forgiveness.

01:26.545 --> 01:31.050
May God grant you
pardon and peace.

01:31.050 --> 01:34.053
I absolve you
of your sins.

01:39.642 --> 01:42.603
[Bunchy] Why don't you tell us
how you got here, Ray?

01:49.026 --> 01:51.487
How I got here?

01:51.487 --> 01:54.406
Yeah.

01:54.406 --> 01:55.950
It's usually a good place
to start

01:55.950 --> 01:58.118
the first time
you're talking.

02:00.371 --> 02:02.081
[helicopter blades whirring]

02:02.081 --> 02:05.335
[man mumbling]

02:05.335 --> 02:09.672
[Ray] I guess I got here
same as all you.

02:09.672 --> 02:13.133
Just, uh,

02:13.133 --> 02:17.304
took me a little longer
to figure some things out.

02:17.304 --> 02:20.307
Took meeting Father Romero,

02:20.307 --> 02:23.143
asking for forgiveness.

02:23.143 --> 02:24.353
[groans]

02:24.353 --> 02:28.107
