02:28.107 --> 02:30.943
[priest] ...and their children
are a blessing.

02:30.943 --> 02:34.029
Turn from evil
and do good,

02:34.029 --> 02:37.367
and you will live
in the land forever.

02:37.367 --> 02:38.701
[helicopter blades whirring]

02:38.701 --> 02:41.204
