right from wrong.

02:41.204 --> 02:45.208
They have made God law
their own,

02:45.208 --> 02:47.626
so they will never
slip from His path.

02:47.626 --> 02:49.211
[groans]

02:49.211 --> 02:52.840
[priest] Though they stumble,
they will never fall,

02:52.840 --> 02:55.175
for the Lord holds them
by the hand.

02:55.175 --> 02:58.470
[helicopter blades whirring]

03:16.322 --> 03:21.327
[priest] He will turn from evil
and do good.

03:21.327 --> 03:24.372
He will never abandon
the godly.

03:24.372 --> 03:27.625
He will keep them safe
forever.

03:27.625 --> 03:30.420
