the land...

03:30.420 --> 03:31.670
[groans]

03:31.670 --> 03:33.672
[priest] ...and will live there
forever.

03:33.672 --> 03:37.217
[sighs]

03:37.217 --> 03:40.388
The godly offer good counsel.

03:40.388 --> 03:45.393
...law their own, so they
will never slip from His path.

03:45.393 --> 03:48.812
[priest continues faintly]

03:48.812 --> 03:52.608
