generous loans to others...

03:52.608 --> 03:54.902
...in the land forever.

03:54.902 --> 03:57.321
For the Lord loves justice,

03:57.321 --> 04:00.407
and he will never abandon
the godly.

04:00.407 --> 04:03.077
He will keep them safe forever,

04:03.077 --> 04:05.871
