04:37.444 --> 04:40.239
Hey, man.
How you doing?

04:40.239 --> 04:42.950
You ever been
to Big Bear?

04:42.950 --> 04:44.910
No.

04:44.910 --> 04:47.746
Got a quiet place up there
where I train.

04:47.746 --> 04:51.459
Gonna take you there,
help you recover.

04:52.876 --> 04:55.337
Where's my brother?
Where's Terry?

04:55.337 --> 04:57.172
Terry survived.

04:57.172 --> 04:58.298
He's still in the hospital,
but he's awake.

04:58.298 --> 04:59.299
I gotta go.

04:59.299 --> 05:01.301
I spoke with your wife, Ray.

05:01.301 --> 05:03.220
Police came to your house,

05:03.220 --> 05:05.305
