06:57.626 --> 06:59.629
How do you know Romero?

06:59.629 --> 07:01.547
Same way as you.

07:03.549 --> 07:06.636
You and me been through it,
man.

07:06.636 --> 07:09.888
Punch and donuts
after First Friday,

07:09.888 --> 07:12.516
holding the prayer book,

07:12.516 --> 07:15.143
bringing the wine,

07:15.143 --> 07:17.480
bringing the body.

07:20.065 --> 07:22.485
